{"tid":2193410,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"日本富豪自爆炒股輸44億日圓 Twitter po文反省","createTime":"2020-09-07T22:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T00:33:38.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"82e5123a116bce0cededa7940cf8424f7e39d1d9","tid":2193410,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T22:50:41.000Z","msg":"（中央社東京7日綜合外電報導）日本富豪前澤友作6日在推特表示，因武漢肺炎造成股市急速波動，他被迷惑雙眼，進行多次不熟練的短線交易，結果損失44億日圓（約新台幣12.4億元），他對此「深刻反省」。<br />\n<br />\n前澤友作說，有44億的話，不知道可以發錢給多少人、拯救多少人，他後悔莫及，絕對要用自己的生意把這些損失賺回來。<br />\n<br />\n44歲的前澤友作是大型流行時尚零售網站Zozotown創辦人，他5月時表示，因武漢肺炎疫情影響民生，為了協助單親家庭紓困，設立一個「前澤單親應援基金」，針對1萬名單親爸爸或單親媽媽，每人發10萬日圓。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009070275.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202009070275.aspx&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqEYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=496f0e0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009070275.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"a4d387a057a682798ef07e94dcfadb7e4c5cb9f2","tid":2193410,"uid":20641,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T23:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EwHLPXi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEwHLPXi.jpg&h=0224c308&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1002d5dab9c54e87b7b77c7687e1692de87ae6b6","tid":2193410,"uid":258479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T00:09:50.000Z","msg":"姐係鬼'暗'眼??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb571c823a98361afbf1e7fd8c0354a903594fcb","tid":2193410,"uid":156511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4d387a057a682798ef07e94dcfadb7e4c5cb9f2","tid":2193410,"uid":20641,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T23:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EwHLPXi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu